    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there\u2019s not a single blemish to be found. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
