    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2001 BMW M3 (E46) that serves as a benchmark for the chassis. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a whisper-quiet Vanos system. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, offering surgical gear selection. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry with OEM+ components. The factory finish is immaculate, devoid of any swirling or imperfections, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
